<br>
50 won't get you much.  You might find an old GeForce (original) card at that price.  Supports hardware T&amp;L at it's bare minimums but won't have much life left in it.<br>
<br>
The top of the line cards today are the GeForce 3 based cards.  The lowest end card is the GeForce3 ti200 which sells for about 150, and the high end card is the GeForce3 ti500 which is priced about 350 right now.<br>
<br>
